Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.73,0:21:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别一副苦瓜脸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.57,0:21:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必须一直当我的对手才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.83,0:21:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.83,0:21:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 祝你们幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.52,0:21:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.74,0:21:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.93,0:21:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.40,0:21:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？咦？怎么好象越弄越好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.23,0:21:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玛～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.21,0:22:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 下次我一定更加…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.54,0:22:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森里萤一…本以为是个普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.60,0:22:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到还真有一手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.47,0:22:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一 早上了 今天也是晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.99,0:22:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.67,0:23:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么菲尔德和萤一会…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.02,0:24:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们从过去就一直在交往啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.03,0:24:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 夺回萤一
